Yet Another Gears OpenGL demo
-----------------------------

The yagears package contains a version of the popular gears OpenGL demo (with
OpenGL ES 1.1 CM and 2.0 ports) that supports multiple graphic renderers:

  - GLX interface (OpenGL Extension to the X Window System)
  - DirectFBGL interface (OpenGL Extension for DirectFB)
  - GLFBDev interface (OpenGL Extension to the Linux Framebuffer)
  - EGL interface with X11 display
  - EGL interface with DirectFB display
  - EGL interface with Linux Framebuffer display
  - EGL interface with Wayland display
  - EGL interface with DRM display

and multiple graphical user interfaces:

  - EFL (Enlightenment Foundation Libraries)
  - FLTK (Fast Light ToolKit)
  - GLUT (OpenGL Utility Toolkit)
  - GTK+ (Gimp ToolKit)
  - Qt (Q toolkit)
  - SDL (Simple Directmedia Layer)
  - SFML (Simple and Fast Multimedia Library)
  - wxWidgets (Windows X Widgets)

Have fun,

Nicolas Caramelli
